	/**
	 * Sets the value of a specific field of this scene description node object.
	 * The type of the value to be set depends on the type of the field.<br>
	 * The timestamp of the field will be updated to the current time.
	 * @param name Name of the field to be changed
	 * @param value Value to assign to the specified field
	 * @return True, if succeeded
	 *
	 * Example:
	 * @code
	 * // Predefined initialization function which is called once to initialize this script.
	 * function onOceanInitialize(engine, timestamp)
	 * {
	 *     var sceneNode = ocean.sceneDescription.findNode("CONE");
	 *
